{"tid":1798791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共嚴正反駁《華盛頓郵報》一篇報道，指標題偏頗及誤導，報道中的指控亦無事實根據。","createTime":"2019-12-26T13:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T01:43:27.000Z","uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2c05c50a423458605dae9c6473b55cb67f65114c","tid":1798791,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府嚴正反駁《華盛頓郵報》一篇報道，指標題偏頗及誤導，報道中的指控亦無事實根據。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》刊登一篇以「香港警方處理示威活動時屢次違反指引，未曾面對後果」為題的報道，邀請9名國際專家，根據記者所取得的警隊內部一些使用武力與槍械的指引，評論警隊在印尼女記者右眼中彈及水炮車射中清真寺等事件中，所使用的武力是否合法，專家認為七成行動涉違規。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府發言人傍晚發稿，反駁報道的指控沒有事實根據，對此深表遺憾，強調警方一直秉持嚴謹克制態度，只用最低所需武力，應對示威者公然的違法行為，所使用的武力亦符合國際標準，所有警務人員均需為其所使用的武力負責，指揮官亦在現場監察，確保人員合法使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374657&amp;fbclid=IwAR1BMnKnktx1eMLvDfc7V5SQF_0RCp_wucPTZwDAa4Q3CXMJwOp3JIvMVgw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374657%26fbclid%3DIwAR1BMnKnktx1eMLvDfc7V5SQF_0RCp_wucPTZwDAa4Q3CXMJwOp3JIvMVgw&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=194c5fb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374657%26fbclid%3DIwAR1BMnKnktx1eMLvDfc7V5SQF_0RCp_wucPTZwDAa4Q3CXMJwOp3JIvMVgw&h=2f0ca213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374657&amp;fbclid=IwAR1BMnKnktx1eMLvDfc7V5SQF_0RCp_wucPTZwDAa4Q3CXMJwOp3JIvMVgw</a>"},{"pid":"91589a8111b490dafe380b998471bccadf70c548","tid":1798791,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"Facebook洗地組正式成立！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798781</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a2df24e42d41a74537e3a5a5768f53db9e8398f","tid":1798791,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920e17d68fc2562dff39105680a5c5ba04a2967b","tid":1798791,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"今日仲係紅日咁勤力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e25957e3e7d5e33d960ca0666f8128bfc6cd51","tid":1798791,"uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"特區政府反對 譴責 遺憾=事實<br />\n特區政府贊成 正正顯示 會繼續努力=官商鄉黑警勾結做緊犯法野<br />\n<br />\n林奠衝出黎=宣布仆街野<br />\n張廢宗出黎=錄音機回帶"},{"pid":"e6808e496e8cf21c4ab2fa39a7374c1358c57e23","tid":1798791,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:13:19.000Z","msg":"姐係話人地報fake news 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316f85b81e5230229d7be92a5208a5bb74ec4eb6","tid":1798791,"uid":315191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"特區政府從來唔覺得有錯，錯在市民身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4f661ae2f2697fbfc954b9062e534843077e1f","tid":1798791,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316f85b81e5230229d7be92a5208a5bb74ec4eb6","tid":1798791,"uid":315191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"特區政府從來唔覺得有錯，錯在市民身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:20:54.000Z","msg":"路透社: 香港「逃犯條例」 幕後推手是中紀委<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792110</a>"},{"pid":"562d2830dd69fb7b0686c1b27272f09b5998062f","tid":1798791,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"印尼女記者 毛漢 清真寺呢啲有晒片都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba66b99409f5b704b7df3427002025b0168023d","tid":1798791,"uid":51620,"l