15:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b03f7a638bbe5c315cb2c4cba494443db225d91","tid":1798791,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"耿爽式回應"},{"pid":"1aa12343141873417eecc823e739228b28a69ad2","tid":1798791,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b03f7a638bbe5c315cb2c4cba494443db225d91","tid":1798791,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"耿爽式回應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qMYub9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qMYub9.gif&h=bc3ca129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f85a6617cf8f3501cf7fe704c216c9bf577e8dee","tid":1798791,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"人哋信外媒都唔信香港政府啦，因為講得太多大話⋯⋯遲啲有機會國際成立一個獨立調查委員會嚟調查香港警暴及政府嘅反人類罪⋯⋯到時你地全部都要受制裁⋯⋯"},{"pid":"52d3b3e92c44d9b0267ffeff5f13a7bda92b7df3","tid":1798791,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"愈黎愈似支那口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1ef9f6330845b091d7f2a376c3e64f573cdb83","tid":1798791,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:56:53.000Z","msg":"我唔直接答<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》（英語：The Washington Post）是美國華盛頓哥倫比亞特區具影響力與發行量大的報紙之一，共獲得47座普立茲獎，其中 2008 年獲得獨立的 6 項普立茲獎，僅次於《紐約時報》在 2002 年創下的一份報紙獲得獨立的 7 項普立茲獎的記錄。郵報總部位於華府K街富蘭克林廣場，七十年代初期郵報記者領導了美國媒體對水門事件醜聞的調查性報導，主要導致了尼克森總統的辭職，郵報因此名聲大振。《華盛頓郵報》擅長報導美國國內政治動態，自由派和保守派的均有在華盛頓郵報撰寫專欄。"},{"pid":"fbe200810893350e2361d784f761ac7bad578962","tid":1798791,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"去美國告佢誹謗囉"},{"pid":"6e1fb705dceedb12cc806c0a837d31d3888bfa16","tid":1798791,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"983949cf6a1aa497d50fa36c1b64b6e140bb9799","tid":1798791,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"美國出聲了 ，警察仲唔收斂d？"},{"pid":"50933955345797004c031c53fdaaf135152bbd5b","tid":1798791,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"港共: 雖然我駁唔到,但一定係你哋誤導<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1116b4e79f852ee5509649951e16fa11440011b7","tid":1798791,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50933955345797004c031c53fdaaf135152bbd5b","tid":1798791,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"港共: 雖然我駁唔到,但一定係你哋誤導<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"2c4f661ae2f2697fbfc954b9062e534843077e1f","tid":1798791,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:20:54.000Z","msg":"路透社: 香港「逃犯條例」 幕後推手是中紀委<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792110</a>"}}